**Better at a glance**
- Calorie ring now shows a live percentage and updates in real time when you log food
- Four macros tracked (added fibre), with colour-coded bars that are easier to read
- Three health metrics side-by-side: steps, calories burned, and resting heart rate

**Easier food logging**
- Four meal shortcards (Breakfast / Lunch / Dinner / Snack) show what's been logged at a glance — tap any to open that meal's log
